<kml>
<property-doc name=Position-for-Follow-On>
<system-documentation name=Position-for-Follow-On>
<gpd-documentation name=CritiqueScores>

<description>
Commanders always consider the next step that will most likely be required after the objective is taken and try to position their forces favorably to continue the mission.
</description>

<example>
Is this mission known for the next phase of the operation?<br><br>
Do the forces in this COA finish in a position favorable to continuing the mission into the next phase?<br><br>
</example>

</kml>
